Package: easyRasch2jmv
Type: Package
Title: easyRasch2 for Jamovi
Version: 0.2.5
Date: 2026-04-28
Author: Magnus Johansson
Maintainer: Magnus Johansson <pgmj@pm.me>
Description:   Provides Rasch analysis functions for Jamovi, wrapping analysis logic from the
  easyRasch2 R package. Includes conditional item infit, item-restscore, and
  partial gamma DIF from the iarm package, Yen's Q3 residuals from package mirt,
  and item probability curves (PCM) from eRm. Uses CML estimation from eRm,
  except for the analysis of Q3 residuals, which use MML estimation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    jmvcore (>= 0.8.5),
    R6,
    eRm,
    iarm,
    mirt,
    psychotools (>= 0.7-3),
    stats,
    ggplot2,
    ggdist,
    scales,
    rlang,
    patchwork
